              ></path></g
            ></svg
          >
        </div>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="flex justify-center border border-foreground bg-muted rounded-r-xl px-6 py-6 md:py-5 w-5/6 md:w-auto hover:opacity-80"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold">ABOUT</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-light">
            Find out why I started this project
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-4 flex items-center ml-5">
          <svg
            version="1.1"
            class="!w-full !h-full"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="currentColor"
